column2: An initiating, pioneering energy. Independent, bold, courageous, assertive, fiery, inspirational, direct, and decisive. Can be egotistical, impulsive, impatient, aggressive, or lacking in subtlety.
Stable, enduring, unyielding, earthy, and acquisitive, with strong values and desires. Can be stuck, stubborn, overly possessive, and self-indulgent.
Agile, versatile, inquisitive, flowing, conversational, and airy, with many ideas. Can be volatile, superficial, changeable, restless, and inconsistent.
Nurturing, protective, tenacious, emotionally sensitive, watery, and deeply rooted. Can be overly protective, unwilling to let go, timid, and reclusive.
Self-confident, generous, warm-hearted, powerful, leaderly, and dramatic. Can be overly proud, vain, extravagant, and arrogant.
Meticulous, discriminating, pure, practical, health-conscious, and hard-working. Can be hyper-critical, petty, and perfectionistic.
Even-handed, harmonious, artistic, diplomatic, and balancing, with a strong sense of fairness. Can be overly compromising, appeasing, and judgmental.
Intense and magnetic, with penetrating perception and the power to confront. Can be destructive, vengeful, jealous, and overly dramatic.
Inspiring, enthusiastic, goal-seeking, truthful, and adventurous, with a broad vision. Can be reckless, unrestrained, and tactless.
Disciplined, responsible, reliable, industrious, conscientious, practical, and achieving. Can be pessimistic, overly conventional, rigid, materialistic, and callous.
Humanitarian, innovative, group-conscious, progressive, and service-oriented. Can be rebellious, eccentric, aloof, emotionally superficial, and overly extroverted.
Compassionate, sensitive, self-sacrificing, gentle, and intuitive. Can be escapist, impractical, hypersensitive, and gullible.
